---
import { persona } from "../persona"
import Link from "./Link.astro"
---

<footer class='w-full py-8 text-l/primary dark:text-d/primary'>
  <div class='flex flex-col gap-5 md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between'>
    <div class='max-w-xl space-y-3'>
      <p
        class='font-mono text-[0.68rem] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-l/tertiary dark:text-d/accent'
      >
        Contact
      </p>
      <h3
        class='font-display text-5xl leading-[0.9] tracking-[-0.04em] text-l/primary dark:text-d/primary md:text-6xl'
      >
        Si une idée mérite d’être construite, on peut en parler.
      </h3>
      <p class='text-base leading-8 text-l/secondary dark:text-d/muted'>
        Je travaille entre missions, produits et expérimentations. Si tu veux me
        montrer un projet ou juste m’envoyer un signal, l’e-mail reste la route
        la plus simple.
      </p>
    </div>

    <Link
      target='_self'
      url={`mailto:${persona.email}`}
      noDecorate
      class='font-mono text-[0.72rem] uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-l/primary dark:text-d/primary'
    >
      {persona.email.replace("@", "[@]")}
    </Link>
  </div>

  <p class='mt-8 text-sm text-l/secondary dark:text-d/muted'>
    Ou me retrouver ici :
    {
      persona.contacts.map((c) => (
        <span class="uppercase after:content-['_/_'] last:after:content-none">
          <Link
            target='_blank'
            url={c.url}
            noDecorate
            class='mx-1 font-mono text-[0.68rem] uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-l/primary dark:text-d/primary'
          >
            {c.title}
          </Link>
        </span>
      ))
    }
  </p>
</footer>
